Wait a minute,
isn't that just a sound effect?

20:53.902 --> 20:57.646
No, it's got to be real.
Right, Lizzo?

20:57.648 --> 21:01.908
Uh, seems a bit excessive to me,
but, hey, pshh, you're the kid.

21:01.910 --> 21:03.928
You know what?
If you're uncomfortable,

21:03.930 --> 21:06.171
-you don't have to do it.
-(Homer sighs)

21:06.173 --> 21:08.582
I could do it for you.
And action!

21:08.584 --> 21:11.269
-(grunts)
-Maybe a few more for safety?

21:11.271 --> 21:12.495
(Homer grunting)

21:12.497 --> 21:15.422
Whose safety? (grunts)
I don't feel safe!

21:15.424 --> 21:18.167
-(rhythmic slapping)
-Ow. Ow.

21:18.169 --> 21:19.518
Why, you little...

21:19.520 --> 21:20.669
-This beat is fire.
-(Homer continues grunting)

21:20.671 --> 21:23.839
Yo, Lisa, how 'bout
I get Sasha Flute,

21:23.841 --> 21:25.841
you get your saxamaphone,

21:25.843 --> 21:27.843
and we, uh, jam?

21:27.845 --> 21:29.528
I'd love to.

21:29.530 --> 21:31.847
-(playing<i> Simpsons</i> theme)
-Ow. Ow.

21:31.849 --> 21:34.500
Ow. Stop that.

21:35.853 --> 21:37.778
Ow. Ow.

21:37.780 --> 21:41.507
Ow. Ow. Ow.

21:43.027 --> 21:44.860
Why, you little...

21:44.862 --> 21:46.862
Ow.

21:46.864 --> 21:48.264
(music ends)

21:49.291 --> 21:50.141
Shh!
